<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A AW KA HNGALH CH204</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka Khamhtu ka hmu lo na-in, Nifa ka sin-ah bia a chim, Ka Bawi ah ka
 thim cang ca-ah, Bawipa thangthat a aw ka hngalh.

[C1]
   A aw ka hngalh Ka Khamhtu aw, Lunglawmh thanuamh nak a ka pek, Bia a
   ka ruah tik-ah ka lawm, Bawipa thangthat, A aw ka hngalh.

[V2]
 A muisam ka hmu lo na-in, Thlichia lak-ah a aw ka theih, Tilet cu dai
 u, a ti hna, Ni a tlang i zeizong an dai.

[C2]
   A aw ka hngalh Ka Khamhtu aw, Lunglawmh thanuamh nak a ka pek, Bia a
   ka ruah tik-ah ka lawm, Bawipa thangthat, A aw ka hngalh.

[V3]
 Bia-tak le bia ding a ka chimn, Mit hmuh lo lawmhnak le dinhnak,
 Hna-ngam dawtnak kong a ka chimh, Vancung inn dawh kong a ka chimh.

[C3]
   A aw ka hngalh Ka Khamhtu aw, Lunglawmh thanuamh nak a ka pek, Bia a
   ka ruah tik-ah ka lawm, Bawipa thangthat, A aw ka hngalh.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>204</hymn_number>
</song>